(65022, 153171, 0, 1, 'So Far Away', '', '2013-06-30 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 2, 7, '血液在我身體燃燒　麻痺\n麻痺了自己　我彷彿快要窒息\n我抗拒不了回憶　沉默不語\n是為了想停止再嘆息\n\nI cant take it no more.\nWhen my dream and my faith...\nWhen I try to ran away...\nI hear your voice with me.\nPlease give me a sign....\n\nCause You''re so far away.\nI cant feel it.\nDont go away.\nStay with me...\nStay with me....\n\nIts time...Time to for my test.\nThis time...I nerver ever quiet.\nIt just a test for me.\nIt just a test for my load.\n\nI hear your voice with me...\nPlease give me a sign.\n\nCause You''re so far away.\nI cant feel it.\nDont go away.\nStay with me...\n\nSo I keep....driving.....', '', 344, '', '', '', '', '情緒壓縮', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-06-30 13:37:05', '2015-03-12 14:01:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
